Liquor Store: Welcome! If you have any questions
about sake, feel free to ask.

Liquor Store: Huh? Recently, there's been a
citrus-flavored sparkling sake in commercials?

Liquor Store: ...Ah, you mean Stelk ZERO. Sorry,
but we're almost out of stock right now...
Well then, if it's just the remaining stock...

Liquor Store: Sorry, but there's a reservation to
buy the remaining stock at a high price... I don't
know when the next shipment will arrive, so we'll
just have to wait for that.

Liquor Store: They said they would pay this
much... *whispering*

Liquor Store: Well... if they're willing to pay
more than that, I might consider it...

(...I really want it right away... but luck isn't
on my side... Well... even if it's expensive, it's
not an amount I can't afford...)

(Are there any other materials I can negotiate
with...?)

(....\.\.There's...\.\.one thing....... Let's make
a firm decision before we negotiate....)

Liquor Store Owner: Oh, you're here again. If
you're going to buy, do it soon.
Negotiating with our bodies\c[0] (Required lewdness level: 15)

Liquor Store Owner: ...If you're going to spend
that much, I guess I have no choice. In
return...I'll do it for you secretly.
I got my hands on Stelk ZERO!

(Just for a single bottle of liquor...! It's no
joke, it's an expensive purchase... But if I can
obtain psychic powers with this, then it's a cheap
deal...)
(Well, let's go back to Rei-san's place)

The liquor store's H event has been added to the
flashback.

(Hmm... It's difficult to negotiate with my
current financial situation...)
\c[27]身体で交渉する\c[0](必要淫乱度:15)

(...What am I thinking...! There's no way I can do
something so indecent...!)

Liquor Store Owner: Hehe... I'll count on you
again...
